# Local dev link targets for the portal's three house cards.
# Loaded by `astro dev` (development mode) only; production builds use the
# real-domain defaults in src/pages/index.astro. Ports match each app's
# astro.config server.port (jet 4321, yacht 4322, provisioning 4323).
PUBLIC_JET_URL=http://localhost:4321
PUBLIC_YACHT_URL=http://localhost:4322
PUBLIC_PROV_URL=http://localhost:4323
